# ease-pulse-fast: Rapid Pulse for Urgent States

A faster version of ease-pulse with 0.5s cycle instead of 2s, designed for critical alerts and urgent UI states.

## Classes

| Class | Effect |
|-------|--------|
| `ease-pulse-fast` | Rapid opacity pulse (0.5s) |
| `ease-pulse-fast-scale` | Rapid scale pulse (0.5s) |
| `ease-pulse-fast-glow` | Rapid glow pulse (0.5s) |
| `ease-pulse-fast-dot` | Pulsing dot indicator |

### Color Variants
| Class | Color |
|-------|-------|
| `ease-pulse-fast-red` | #ef4444 |
| `ease-pulse-fast-amber` | #f59e0b |
| `ease-pulse-fast-green` | #22c55e |
| `ease-pulse-fast-blue` | #3b82f6 |

## Usage

```html
<!-- Pulsing badge -->
<span class="ease-pulse-fast ease-pulse-fast-red">CRITICAL</span>

<!-- Dot indicator -->
<span class="ease-pulse-fast-dot ease-pulse-fast-red"></span>

<!-- Glow button -->
<button class="ease-pulse-fast-glow ease-pulse-fast-red">Alert</button>
```

## Customization

```css
:root {
  --ease-pulse-fast-color: #ef4444;
}
```

## Features
- 0.5s rapid cycle vs ease-pulse's 2s
- 3 variants: opacity, scale, glow
- 4 color variants
- Pulsing dot indicator
- Respects prefers-reduced-motion